Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:11.45,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Okay, it's reward time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.93,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.66,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.30,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Dostoevsky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.75,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Looks like difficult reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.86,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}When I was a university student, I also challenged myself with that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.48,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But I got lost in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:07.35,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Russian literature has so many names that appear again and again-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.10,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}-that I had such a difficult time keeping everyone separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.71,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That's the first smile I've seen from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.61,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’re a rather pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.11,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, no... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.05,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.42,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ll bet your boyfriend loves to boast about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.01,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No... I don’t have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.44,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're kidding! When you're this pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:40.00,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If that's true, then the boys at this school really have poor taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.59,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But somewhere in this school there should be a boy you like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:51.06,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There is! Tell me, what kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.45,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's probably someone who likes books, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.16,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:05.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Well, I won't force you to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.03,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}but you can come talk to me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.00,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're the type to find true romantic love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.03,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so I'll give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.06,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This time it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.28,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's going into the p*ssy you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.48,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:06:00.08,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I can also feel it in my p*ssy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.00,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.03,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}is not much of a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:22.01,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I can't believe how much she can take!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:26.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This is the largest size and we got three in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.35,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now, birth them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.34,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.76,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Do you happen to know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:28.21,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The secretary, Hiraishi-san, was the last person here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:33.43,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We checked all the classrooms many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.92,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}One man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:45.00,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Whereas the women were all different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:46.68,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The more I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.53,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}it has to be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.39,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As the victims are all members of the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.03,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}no one else could do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.57,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Moreover, as I pick at this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:12.80,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}So pitiful... can't come out of depression... how could the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:29.01,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You haven't been coming to the library lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.41,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.95,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm just busy with my after-school job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's Midaigawa Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.91,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh! From the well-known family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:13.57,Blind Night Book Title,,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(436,128)\frx332\fry26\fscx78.8\fscy87.5\frz32.4}Crime and Punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:18.03,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I read it in middle school, but it was difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.42,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm re-reading it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.03,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I read that about six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.32,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's a very deep and wonderful book, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.83,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I liked the old you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.21,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.39,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But now you’re obsessed with getting attention and adoration from everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.01,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Does it really make you that happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.15,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Master... and that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.67,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don't lay a hand on useless women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.57,Blind Night Book Title,,0,0,0,,{\be1\frz46.2\pos(574,454)\fscx124\fscy130\frx6\fry358}Crime and Punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.02,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was asked my name... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.07,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.36,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.18,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}A bibliomaniac student? {Note: I chose bibliomaniac because dokushozuki is a lot less casual than just someone who likes books.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:48.57,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Exactly. It would be great if you could remember a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.36,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.12,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:05.30,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Apart from the people the librarian told me about,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.30,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}there's this name stamped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.01,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Mutsuki Jouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:59.15,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sister, I heard there was something you want to tell me. What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.76,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The student congress president, Shiina Mizuho-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:07.03,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}wants you to become one of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:12.86,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To make our Master the ruler of this school, you can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.15,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.65,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:59.56,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This is the best! I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.28,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}More, please be rougher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.11,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.76,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Stop pestering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:17.01,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Have you forgotten that you are my slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.66,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:33.64,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It was my fault. I was impertinent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.51,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The people I hate most are those who try to score points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.87,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To change that kind of attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.74,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}we have to purify the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.74,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.57,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This is one part of a larger ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.33,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You must surmount this or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.81,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.74,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:15.07,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No, I mean, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Push it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:16.28,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:43.02,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Here, your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.51,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Who will be the next sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:21.44,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Such a lovely smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.02,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He can't possibly be related to the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:44.02,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder if he's looking at the same starry sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:51.36,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wish that I could have the same conversation with him about books,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:55.02,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That I had with Ichijou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:03.01,Blind Night Dialogue Alt.,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Why am I such an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:12.07,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What do you plan to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:15.12,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Do you honestly think you’ll get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:18.06,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sensei, you're the one at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:20.23,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You were sniffing around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.17,0:24:23.09,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're behind all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:27.08,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I thought you had the power of a magic circle, but that was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.13,0:24:30.69,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You and everyone are merely under someone else’s hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:36.99,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Midaigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:39.43,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The reason why everyone adores you now-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.49,0:24:42.01,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}-is because they finally came to see how wonderful you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.62,0:24:48.00,Blind Night Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's the true power that was sleeping inside of you.
